{"tid":2201882,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警供稱被告被捕時「個身左右搖擺」　惟影片拍不到","createTime":"2020-09-14T07:00:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T08:53:14.000Z","uid":6497,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0926ccbad4f4de45dc0e5b8be9b9309b6837579a","tid":2201882,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T07:00:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200914/VG2YTGZ7TBHSTOPNEE24VUAIM4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200914%2FVG2YTGZ7TBHSTOPNEE24VUAIM4%2F&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8Mls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=b27b8a21\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200914%2FVG2YTGZ7TBHSTOPNEE24VUAIM4%2F&h=a10fe393\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200914/VG2YTGZ7TBHSTOPNEE24VUAIM4/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HIPVWMgzOIbPmLLPOcBHQTlPo0o=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/C5V74UGEEBHLTM76BKCJSOUZGA.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHIPVWMgzOIbPmLLPOcBHQTlPo0o%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FC5V74UGEEBHLTM76BKCJSOUZGA.jpeg&h=c2d983a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黑警陳樂謙<br />\n<br />\n去年10月30日警⽅大興行動基地疑有不明氣體洩漏，大批居民和⽰威者聚集附近抗議，警方同晚作出驅散並截停23歲男侍應，在其身上搜到雷射筆。侍應今就參與非法集結及在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器兩罪受審。制服被告的警員供稱，當時從後截停被告，被告掙扎及糾纏。然而辯方播出影片，顯示被告與警員當日是面對面接觸，被告沒有掙扎，警員看畢片段後指：「被告個身左右搖擺」，惟他同意影片拍不到被告身體左右擺動。<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，被告不作供，明天結案陳詞。"},{"pid":"330445ba4d74db555fda1b82f16a0667574e66e9","tid":2201882,"uid":14941,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T07:01:03.000Z","msg":"頭搖又尾擺"},{"pid":"404072e4f4b428ac72b259648519f6b714e44b6c","tid":2201882,"uid":23919,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T07:01:56.000Z","msg":"不如話條鳩fing下fing下啦<im